Business Strategy And Team Work
YAQSMAN GLOBAL SERVICES LIMITED Carriers our turnkey projects in association with joint venture partners engaged fully in the construction industry. This enables the company to pool together materials and labour resources to achieve set goals at lesser cost. Thus in all projects, selection of approximately qualified personnel and equipment become relatively easier.

SERVICE WARRANTY

PROJECT OBJECTIVES AND MISSION STATEMENT
YAQSMAN GLOBAL SERVICES LIMITED recognizes that well defined, understood and agreed upon objectives are essential to the successful execution of a project. Accordingly, a list of objectives following the start of work has been established.
ü  Furniture making and marketing locally and internationally.
ü  Achieve the highest level of managerial and operational resources dedicated to the project
ü  Attain the quickest possible start in project execution and improve the target start up dates of both phases.
ü  Attain a cost effective plan design throughout
ü  Achieve a safety record better than historical performances.
PROJECT TEAM CONCEPT
Team work concept has been the first insight of YAQSMAN GLOBAL SERVICES LIMIED. We believe in working together with one mind, from various department quotes contribution in every project, in order to work in the company general vision and mission statement.

PROJECT MANAGEMENT AND ENGINEERING ORGANISATION
Our management team have full participation when it comes to such large turnkey project in order meet up standard and specifications. We have professionals that are well organized in various fields of engineering, with over 10 years’ experience in managing and coordinating projects of such.

PROCUREMENT, EXPEDITING AND INSPECTION
Procurement services include obtaining quotations for requisitions, computerized bid evaluation, order preparation and order placing. The purchasing responsibility include obtaining and screening of vendors suborder for inspection purposes, processing and expediting of all manufacturer data. Including drawings. Maintenance instructions and test certificates. Purchasing of major equipment is handled by experienced buyers. YAQSMAN GLOBAL SERVICE LIMITED Carryout its expending and inspection services through its local branches, using qualified professional expediters and coordination of foreign supplies is also rest assured.
ADMINISTRATION AND FINANCING
Under the direction of admin and financial manager, we shall be responsible for all the operations concerning the administration services of personnel and materials. The main duties are:
Ø  Official administrating accounting to whole project
Ø  Personnel administration and industrial relation
Ø  Administration and payment of subcontractors and suppliers
Ø Administration of warehouses and materials

The administration department shall also be responsible for implementing and supervising the field administration offices. The financial officer shall be responsible for implementing the project financial planning and control economic resources assigned to the project and worldwide liaison the banks and the company in term of partnership agreement.  
QUALITY CONTROL AND QUALITY ASSURANCE.
Under the direction of the quality control and quality assurance manager, they safeguard and ensure that workforce performed their diligent duties according to the inherent international standards, rules and procedures, and that shall meet the quality requirements by the contract, its attached specifications and special prescriptions.

PROJECT CONTROL
Planning and scheduling-the procedures used by YAQSMAN GLOBAL SERVICES LIMITED for planning and scheduling are in line with the most up-to-date method. Planning Engineers under the direct control of the project controller are appointed to produce and maintain an overall project schedule in accordance with the contract.
CONSTRUCTION SUPERVISION
The goal of YAQSMAN GLOBAL SERVICES LIMITED is to complete project construction within the established schedules, in conformity with the specifications, in most economical way. For this purpose, the field construction force is under the direct management of the construction manager, who supported by his field staff of permanent employees, coordinates, and schedules and supervises all the activities of direct hire labour and/or subcontracted personnel in the field.

CONSTRUCTION
YAQSMAN GLOBAL SERVICES LIMITED is in position of undertaking with in certain areas, construction activities are performed by its own construction plant and equipment. In other areas, construction is subcontracted to reliable local or international firms under YAQSMAN GLOBAL SERVICES LIMITED full responsibility and supervision. A typical construction organizational chart is enclosed at the end of this section.
Ø  Construction equipment maintenance
Ø  Construction phases

CONSTRUCTION EQUIPMENT MAINTENANCE
The construction equipment superintendent shall be responsible for keeping construction equipment in good operation conditions, not only at the central workshop, but also along the construction site locations. To achieve this, he will be assisted by skilled foremen in enough quantity to fulfil construction requirement.  

CONSTRUCTION PHRASES
The construction manager shall be assisted by a construction general superintendent, who will supervise all the construction phases involved. For this task, the construction general superintendent will be supported by foremen, with proved experience in such assignment, to cover the different specialties to execute the works in proper and timely manner.

SAFETY
A safety superintendent, reporting to the construction manager shall be assigned for implementing a comprehensive and intensive safety program for the project development covering all construction activities.
The main goal of the program shall be providing a safe and healthy working environment to the personnel involved, transferring safety and procedures knowledge to subcontractors. All safety rules and procedures shall be audited and supervised by the safety department.

TECHNICAL OFFICE
The technical office manager shall be responsible for supervising the following tasks
Ø  Construction drawings and specification files
Ø  Liaison between the engineering construction groups, in order to coordinate the surveying tasks. Relation with landowners, communities and public entities.

COMMISSIONING AND START-UP
YAQSMAN GLOBAL SERVICES LIMITED will assist the client during commission and start-up by providing special skilled personnel in order to ensure that the plant will meet the process and engineering specification.
